{"tid":1715060,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港預言電影: 《紅Van》","createTime":"2019-11-13T04:01:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T20:58:00.000Z","uid":134071,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"52460278fb248efe8a1d34fd3f3dcc8fccb96fd0","tid":1715060,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:01:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.hkfilmblog.com/archives/72032\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkfilmblog.com%2Farchives%2F72032&d=lZ7jQHZQyV3jEURUmMbLadRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=1f7afa49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkfilmblog.com/archives/72032</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TtLRM9U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTtLRM9U.jpg&h=f0ff7fe3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/POcQigA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPOcQigA.jpg&h=fe738663&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/86whHJg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F86whHJg.jpg&h=cc97a4c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MCevigC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMCevigC.jpg&h=b73e4b66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港預言的電影<br />\nBy Ryan<br />\nOn 13/11/2019<br />\n<br />\nIn 講鏟舊片<br />\n<br />\n過去數天，香港各區均發生警民衝突，而道路亦嚴重受阻。而警方所使用的武力以至手法，亦令人感到心寒。如斯的情況，也許不少人意想不到，不過其實早數年前，已有電影似乎預視到這個情況。<br />\n<br />\n先來看看電影對白，有人說出「大家不要欺騙自己說」。<br />\n<br />\n「外面一切都是正常的」一句，以今時今日的香港，大家有何體會。<br />\n<br />\n熟悉近日警民衝突的朋友，對於旺角彌敦道與亞皆老街交易的惠豐中心，該十分熟悉。<br />\n<br />\n看到如斯裝備的人，大家會聯想到甚麼？是否將當天的況變成現實？<br />\n<br />\n當然，說對方是妖言惑眾的人士，相信大家對於他們的政見立場亦十分清楚。<br />\n<br />\n當然，亦有人叫人覺醒。<br />\n<br />\n這一句，大家是否心同感受？<br />\n<br />\n惠英紅在片中的這一句，是否十分像某位政府女高層的咀臉？<br />\n<br />\n這點，也許是作為香港人的大家最擔心的事吧！<br />\n<br />\n在這個時候，大家有否感到社會法律與仁義道德？<br />\n<br />\n在這裡，已經不重要，因為連我們執法者已無視這個。<br />\n<br />\n大家對這一句，有何感覺？<br />\n<br />\n當年的預告，以「還我香港」為題，未知是否今時今日大家的心聲？<br />\n<br />\n如斯到題的預告，到底是來自哪部電影？答案是：<br />\n<br />\n《那夜凌晨，我坐上了旺角開往大埔的紅Van》，這部是五年前香港國際電影節開幕電影，電影由陳果執導，改編自網上原著。當年預告的對白，到今時今日再看見，卻有另一番感覺。海報上一句「一夜之間，香港沒有了」，再比對昨晚香港中文大學發生的事，未知大家是否有所同感？"},{"pid":"d6d01d93ed296ca9ac04f40ac8ec1353ee4925cc","tid":1715060,"uid":60393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:02:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc894910c8d4196e372d5595084a79598ddccedd","tid":1715060,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:04:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70f0e1e86fd7a4b6e089079f6c64cb58968a26a4","tid":1715060,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:04:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\n<br />\n最新<br />\n<br />\n！！！！Sen. Cory Gardner (Colorado)<br />\n關注中大 支持香港<br />\n！！！！佢未cosponsor條Act 請佢幫忙:bangbang::bangbang:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenCoryGardner/status/1194341990655246346?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenCoryGardner%2Fstatus%2F1194341990655246346%3Fs%3D19&d=lZ7jQHZQyV3jEURUmMbLadRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=9ed60a65\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenCoryGardner%2Fstatus%2F1194341990655246346%3Fs%3D19&h=c0f128d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenCoryGardner/status/1194341990655246346?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n！！Sen Menendez 出聲<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/senatormenendez/status/1194349446349443072?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenatormenendez%2Fstatus%2F1194349446349443072%3Fs%3D21&d=lZ7jQHZQyV3jEURUmMbLadRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=16c947a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenatormenendez%2Fstatus%2F1194349446349443072%3Fs%3D21&h=6fdcee86\" data-auto-link target=\